## Setup Instructions

### Backend (will run on https://localhost:5259/)
open terminal
cd backend
cd TvShowTracker.Api
dotnet restore
dotnet build
dotnet run

### Frontend (will run on http://localhost:5173/)
open terminal
cd frontend
cd tvShowTracker-frontend
npm install
npm run dev
